===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|ls=psc|示|c1=s|t1=altar|羊|c2=p}}. Originally just {{lang|zh|羊}}, {{lang|zh|示}} was added later to distinguish it.

===Etymology===
;"fortune, omen (good or bad)" > "good luck"
:According to {{zh-ref|Schuessler (2007)}}, many different etymologies are theoretically possible:
:*possibly belonging to {{och-l|悆}} ~ {{och-l|譽}} ~ {{och-l|豫|cheerful, joyous}};
:*possibly related to {{cog|bo|གཡང||happiness, blessing, prosperity}} (cf. {{zh-ref|Bodman, 1980}}) (yet see {{zh-l|慶}});
:*Note also {{cog|skb|tr=laaŋᴬ¹|t=luck}}

;ancient funeral sacrifice
